text: Ibrahim Chenihi (born January 24, 1990 in M'Sila) is an Algerian footballer who plays for Damac and the Algeria national team. He plays mainly as a winger, and can play on both wings. ==International career== Chenihi made his debut for the Algeria national team on March 26, 2015, coming on as a second half substitute in a friendly match against Qatar.
